<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Digital Legal Desk</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="images/favicon.png">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }
        .hero {
            background: url('images/banner.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
            height: 60vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
        }
        .hero .overlay {
            background: rgba(0, 47, 108, 0.6);
            padding: 20px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .section {
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .section.alt {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #FF9933, #FFFFFF, #138808);
        }
        .section h2 {
            color: #002868;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .section ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 2;
        }
        .section ul li::before {
            content: "⚖️ ";
        }
        .contact {
            background-color: #eef2f7;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #002868;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Hero Banner -->
    <div class="hero">
        <div class="overlay">
            <h1>Digital Legal Desk</h1>
            <p>Your Trusted Online Legal Solution</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- About Us Section -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>We are a professional online legal service provider, committed to delivering fast, reliable, and affordable legal solutions across India.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Services Section -->
    <div class="section alt">
        <h2>Our Services</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Legal Advice — Talk to our experienced legal consultants online.</li>
            <li>Document Drafting — Affidavits, Agreements, Notices, etc.</li>
            <li>Online Filing — Simplified online legal processes.</li>
            <li>Startup Legal Support — Registrations, Compliance & More.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <div class="contact">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>Phone: +91-XXXXXXXXXX</p>
        <p>Email: info@digitallegaldesk.com</p>
        <p>Website: www.digitallegaldesk.com</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        &copy; 2025 Digital Legal Desk. All Rights Reserved.
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
